---
/**
 * ForCompanies.astro — design-partner CTA block.
 */
---

<section class="px-6 py-24 border-t border-neutral-900">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
    <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-neutral-100 mb-6">
      Running ZeroSync in production?
    </h2>
    <p class="text-neutral-400 leading-relaxed mb-4 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      I'm actively working with design partners building HIPAA / GDPR-sensitive
      collaboration apps. If you need a production license, direct support from
      the maintainer, priority on feature requests, or help with self-hosted
      deployment — let's talk.
    </p>
    <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      Early-stage design partners get meaningful discounts in exchange for
      feedback and, optionally, a case study.
    </p>

    <a
      href="mailto:contact.zerosync@proton.me?subject=ZeroSync%20design%20partner%20inquiry"
      class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 rounded-lg bg-accent text-neutral-950 font-semibold hover:bg-accent-muted hover:text-neutral-950"
    >
      Email contact.zerosync@proton.me
    </a>
  </div>
</section>
